      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Valdobbiadene, Italy</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A reliable Prosecco benchmark with clean pear and apple fruit. It is the right bottle when you want freshness, not autolytic richness, and when the wine needs to stay bright and easy rather than become the center of the table.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Glera</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-100">
